<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf688b824-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s9304"><num value="9304">§ 9304.</num><heading> Pilotage pools</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idf688b825-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s9304/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content> The Secretary may authorize the formation of a pool by a voluntary association of United States registered pilots to provide for efficient dispatching of vessels and rendering of pilotage services.</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idf688b826-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s9304/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><chapeau> For pilotage pools, the Secretary may—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf688b827-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s9304/b/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> limit the number of the pools;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf688b828-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s9304/b/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> prescribe regulations for their operation and administration;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf688b829-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s9304/b/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> prescribe a uniform system of accounts;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf688b82a-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s9304/b/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> perform audits and inspections; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idf688b82b-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s9304/b/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><content> require coordination on a reciprocal basis with similar pool arrangements authorized by the appropriate agency of Canada.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idf688b82c-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/89">Pub. L. 98–89</ref>, <date date="1983-08-26">Aug. 26, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/559">97 Stat. 559</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
