<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section 9304 provides for the formation of a pool by a voluntary association of United States registered pilots to provide for efficient pilotage services.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsection (a) permits the Secretary to authorize formation of United States pilotage pools.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsection (b) sets forth the restrictions and conditions that the Secretary may prescribe for these pools.</p>
</note>
